 problem1：maven update idk回到1.5
 	在pom.xml中
 		 <build>
      	<plugins> 
	<plugin> 
		<groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId> 
		<artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId> 
		<version>2.3.2</version> 
		<configuration> 
		<source>1.7</source> 
		<target>1.7</target> 
		<encoding>UTF-8</encoding> 
		</configuration> 
	</plugin> 
	</plugins>
	</build>      
